{"tid":1342071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［光復香港］7.22凌晨係曆史轉捩點，下一步要點做","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T02:22:29.000Z","uid":60583,"like":219,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"4aabddec849c09f698842f5e618d126aadb7b1e9","tid":1342071,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:13:07.000Z","msg":"經過7.21遊行同抗爭<br />\n香港巿民，特別係和理非<br />\n都睇到所謂勇武係要點做<br />\n<br />\n同時<br />\n元朗發生黑社會襲擊巿民事件<br />\n警察失職<br />\n全港市民怒不可遏之外<br />\n更反映岀<span style=\"color: orange;\">自衛重要性</span><br />\n<br />\n兩者結合<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>香港人對勇武升級嘅心理關卡再低一級</strong></span><br />\n下一步必須宣布<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港政權失效</span></span><br />\n連最基本人身安全權利都無保障<br />\n管治失效<br />\n推番政府係香港人<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">唯一岀路</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n兵貴神速<br />\n香港同香港人已經無時間再等<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">呢3日內必須有第一波行動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n應該光復元朗先？<br />\n定全民罷工入金鐘直攪政府？"},{"pid":"9bf5bd754f07569c32eff6c55d11d98dd51954a0","tid":1342071,"uid":60583,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:13:37.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8518948b53987e93848f2c6743400924f38d6848","tid":1342071,"uid":60583,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:13:47.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"2266e67cbdc9a292e633c8125cb29082b527a387","tid":1342071,"uid":60583,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:13:57.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"efc694ba63845ff54002a1d7efc9324f5f13bee2","tid":1342071,"uid":237143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:14:09.000Z","msg":"罷工搞撚左元朗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff8e5411bc9309978fc646b910433370ecf1f24","tid":1342071,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:14:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg